===Changes from [[2003 Vodacom Cup|2003]]===
*{{Rut Boland Cavaliers}} got relegated from the Vodacom Cup to the Vodacom Shield.
*{{Rut Border Bulldogs}} got promoted from the Vodacom Shield to the Vodacom Cup.

